This are development snapshot, they've many security and stability problems (buffer overflows, ...)
GamerSource won't take responsibility for any  damage made  by this project.

Use it only if you're sure what you do and you've checked the few poor lines of code...

To build the file(s) link it again GL (-lGL) and SDL:

e.g to build the partikels/basics.c file for Linux exectue:
gcc partikels/basics.c -lGL  `sdl-config --cflags --libs` 

